{"tid":1398014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【求置頂】凍資產 奪國藉 禁售武器 加國七大城市抗暴救港","createTime":"2019-08-02T16:07:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T16:17:23.000Z","uid":61242,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cac7aa045f33cce9e8d55d73fefc3a7f2c441507","tid":1398014,"uid":61242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:07:08.000Z","msg":"加國七城聯手 抗暴救港<br />\n<br />\n香港政府漠視民意強推逃犯議案修訂條例，香港人自6月9號起爆發一連串抗議示威活動，堅持五大訴求，缺一不可，政府至今一直未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n及至7月21日晚上十時許，元朗西鐵站內發生過百名白衣人手持武器，無差別襲擊手無寸鐵的無辜市民和抗爭者，在文明社會中此舉已屬恐怖襲擊，惟當晚警方接獲市民報警後，不單未能在承諾15分鐘內到達案發現場的指引，延遲39分鐘才抵達涉事現場，同時被香港及國際傳媒拍下警方與白衣人非比尋常的關係，包括兩名警員對西鐵站對手持武器的白衣人視若無睹，以及警方對手持武器的白衣人放行的畫面，令元朗一夜之間成為「冇警時份」，被懷疑警黑勾結。事後警方只以非法集結罪名拘捕19人，並全數獲准保釋。<br />\n<br />\n同一晚位於上環，對於五大訴求不撤不散的抗爭者，被警方多次在毫無預警下，於行人天橋及林士街停車場等高地，向抗爭者發射多枚催淚彈及橡膠子彈，作不合理驅趕，部份執法警員更拒絕出示委任證。警方當晚拘捕45名市民，其中44名被控暴動罪，當中包括在現場予以救援受傷市民的醫護人員及學生。暴動罪在香港的最高刑罰是監禁十年。<br />\n<br />\n自7.21起，香港警方變本加厲，多次拒絕對申請遊行集會發出不反對通知書，違反基本人權，雖然無阻香港市民及抗爭者上街堅持訴求，惟警方施放對人體有害的過期催淚彈、在警棍加上不明物體予以私刑、荷槍實彈指向市民。繼元朗及上環後，再於馬鞍山、葵涌等地爆發多次衝突，強闖私人物業，並無任何搜查令下無理要求搜證搜捕。<br />\n<br />\n香港警方選擇執法，濫用權力粗暴對待抗爭者，淪為漠視市民訴求的政權機器，侵犯基本自由人權，香港特區政府及中共中央違反《中英聯合聲明》，嚴重蠶食「港人治港、高度自治」，不少加國港人感到痛心、憤怒。為此，一群散落在加國各地的香港人堅決為港集氣發聲，本周末於全國多個城市，包括卡加里、哈里法斯、滿地可、渥太華、多倫多、溫尼辟及溫哥華，參照香港無大台模式，自發舉行街站、連儂牆、集會、遊行，並發出加國城市聯合聲明，支持香港市民堅持五大訴求，缺一不可，承諾持續監察，並向加國政府及國會議員強烈要求，捍衛《中英聯合聲明》對香港人各種自由的保障、制裁及禁止向香港出售及輸出具殺傷力武器、凍結香港特區政府官員及警隊決策高層的加國資產及褫奪國藉、要求加國政府放寬對香港政治犯的入境簽證限制、與中國嚴正交涉立即釋放兩名加國外交官等。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Liberate Hong Kong, it is the revolution of our times.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n一群加國香港人<br />\n<br />\n多倫多 Toronto 3/8<br />\n2:30pm <br />\nMillennium Park, Markham (100 Town Centre Blvd, Markham, Ontario L3R 5H9)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/1762969223847976/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F1762969223847976%2F&d=JkVIzhDRZadGdMc0KemjDRmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=0ef4b16b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/1762969223847976/</a><br />\n<br />\n滿地可 3/8 <br />\n2pm Monument &agrave; Sir George-&Eacute;tienne Cartier, Parc de Mont-Royal<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/453296051889933/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F453296051889933%2F&d=JkVIzhDRZadGdMc0KemjDRmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=eec5ea97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/453296051889933/</a><br />\n<br />\n溫哥華 Vancouver 3/8<br />\n3pm Vancouver Art Gallery North Plaza Square - &scaron;xʷƛ̓ənəq Xwtl&rsquo;e7&eacute;nḵ Square<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/366995924000245/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F366995924000245%2F&d=JkVIzhDRZadGdMc0KemjDRmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=3c6dd967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/366995924000245/</a><br />\n<br />\n卡加里 Calgary 4/8.<br />\n2pm Gather at Chinatown and march to Chinese council<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/658357634628203/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F658357634628203%2F&d=JkVIzhDRZadGdMc0KemjDRmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=1eea62ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/658357634628203/</a><br />\n<br />\n溫尼辟 Winnipeg 3/8 <br />\n5pm Canadian Museum for Human Rights<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/1211402872365957/?ti=icl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F1211402872365957%2F%3Fti%3Dicl&d=JkVIzhDRZadGdMc0KemjDRmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=0d6c6b4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/1211402872365957/?ti=icl</a><br />\n<br />\n哈里法斯 Halifax 3/8, 4/8<br />\n10am-5pm (Opposite to Grand Parade) Barrington St, Halifax<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/676292886183493/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F676292886183493%2F&d=JkVIzhDRZadGdMc0KemjDRmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=32b55ae9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/676292886183493/</a><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N8xFkuk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN8xFkuk.png&h=fd72c1a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ebe25cdb2d1763fe9d060bf309e387919780c0d","tid":1398014,"uid":272355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:09:11.000Z","msg":"有冇人寫信畀政府如果有中國學生搞笑驅逐佢哋出竟"},{"pid":"7776d075fcfaafda3e4ba3bb76bf936fcec803ee","tid":1398014,"uid":153722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:09:40.000Z","msg":"謝 推"},{"pid":"a6344dd6ef70796128f6f8558652cf9b24a69277","tid":1398014,"uid":61242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ebe25cdb2d1763fe9d060bf309e387919780c0d","tid":1398014,"uid":272355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:09:11.000Z","msg":"有冇人寫信畀政府如果有中國學生搞笑驅逐佢哋出竟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:10:02.000Z","msg":"夠膽嚟搞，我哋夠膽做"},{"pid":"0f69b2f367523e6d95eb3938aac29c87e8d6a7fe","tid":1398014,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:10:07.000Z","msg":"假文宣都話要塞三隧！各位小心！！<br />\n<br />\n義士有生命危險！！8月5號有危險，快入！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1392370\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1392370</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>第11頁有藍絲假文宣合集</strong></span><br />\n補番真文宣source<br />\n5/8 全港大三罷+ 7區開🌼 公海<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/saveinghkgrp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsaveinghkgrp&d=JkVIzhDRZadGdMc0KemjDRmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=899756c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/saveinghkgrp</a>"},{"pid":"0a85502c82a4b2f3e4821f5d49b747f768db63df","tid":1398014,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:10:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"791afda3b6fbf0448d594f1f3f100f92d5b3d019","tid":1398014,"uid"